{"tid":787671,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」我成為左連登最多契仔既契爺","createTime":"2018-08-21T00:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T09:00:49.000Z","uid":17866,"like":6,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"734603c0aacd0daa16fc050c0b8ae59115708359","tid":787671,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"終極撚狗系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n與低智區成員對賭，我無1000萬就認曬佢地做契爺加開公道歉，反之我就係否定我有1000萬既人成為我既契仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n契仔名單：<br />\nGreatsoup （首席幫人埋單契弟）<br />\n馬路如苦口<br />\n拿斯屁<br />\nIt狗的日常<br />\n遊雲<br />\n審判專員<br />\n暗黑巨鵰俠<br />\n路人走過<br />\nPonstan<br />\n太窮的後裔<br />\n<br />\n好快兄弟加入，山林道開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時只收到樓樓市gogogo投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講定先，一陣完場實有人出黎話佢無賭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來打打下比賽，有人入場傳波同射龍唔叫參賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n13頁開始大落準契仔落注話我吹水同ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/787067\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/787067</a><br />\n<br />\n34頁開始話人無錢ff,39頁貼完笠左第一次水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/785773 \" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/785773 </a><br />\n<br />\n部分精華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/083518_33cd4469c1d3a1bc1f6470ae228f4832.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F083518_33cd4469c1d3a1bc1f6470ae228f4832.png&h=41165bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/083520_c183bb5b094ab1034bfc4e2ebee8a659.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F083520_c183bb5b094ab1034bfc4e2ebee8a659.png&h=78aa7232&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/083521_6b325b2b300d877cb9fa67ef33250656.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F083521_6b325b2b300d877cb9fa67ef33250656.png&h=b2d81430&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/083522_e98dfc57c104a72dc735a8d5097ce9f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F083522_e98dfc57c104a72dc735a8d5097ce9f1.png&h=27244750&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/083523_1ad6658359e524184858e10d4bd8cc9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F083523_1ad6658359e524184858e10d4bd8cc9e.png&h=28585257&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fc128abc7743ca70017e7e7c35a67a1a06f2a49","tid":787671,"uid":177089,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T00:58:59.000Z","msg":"是但一個契爺post都多過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fdd53c33582f8bad7321565aaa135f60db599a","tid":787671,"uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"樓主型到👍"},{"pid":"1c451462d6909f568accbf8a8b39f088f83bfb25","tid":787671,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1fc128abc7743ca70017e7e7c35a67a1a06f2a49","tid":787671,"uid":177089,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T00:58:59.000Z","msg":"是但一個契爺post都多過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T01:01:31.000Z","msg":"認人做契爺數目多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=