18-08-21T00:58:59.000Z","msg":"是但一個契爺post都多過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T01:01:31.000Z","msg":"認人做契爺數目多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊度單日成交咁多契仔？有無link？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T01:21:40.000Z","msg":"鼝 打到呢個字我認做你老豆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/456125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/456125</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T01:46:10.000Z","msg":"靚波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我轉做收契弟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924894725b89dcc622cef3b9093baca9ab857fcd","tid":787671,"uid":17866,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:55:56.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知老鼠曱甴最難搞係咩?<br />\n你打佢個陣佢就縮,走得快. 你唔打個陣就出來篤眼篤鼻<br />\n咁點打?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/195300_f62800b66397a6433ebe138bfeec598f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F195300_f62800b66397a6433ebe138bfeec598f.jpg&h=a87850c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/195305_c97695703897861e8ee788e04c6373d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F195305_c97695703897861e8ee788e04c6373d0.jpg&h=9415d84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/195421_c97695703897861e8ee788e04c6373d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F195421_c97695703897861e8ee788e04c6373d0.jpg&h=15a15f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n成班打曬飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/195513_d1efaa5c3cbab3a89cc9f3f0a988ded9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F195513_d1efaa5c3cbab3a89cc9f3f0a988ded9.jpg&h=88abe188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用個傳送門, 找數時間11:45<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到晚6點入場收契仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138df62e9ba239e20ac241d80234d0f014c5b229","tid":787671,"uid":71826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"得啦 威啦   <br />\n成地精未?<br />\non9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9e58e7322830ceaa0c893ccad422f7976f83a5","tid":787671,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"138df62e9ba239e20ac241d80234d0f014c5b229","tid":787671,"uid":71826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"得啦 威啦   <br />\n成地精未?<br />\non9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2302e82df7e4693312424177f89aca3e030213a1","tid":787671,"uid":71826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4b9e58e7322830ceaa0c893ccad422f7976f83a5","tid":787671,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"138df62e9ba239e20ac241d80234d0f014c5b